   \n      \n\t语句。\n      \n    解释器对每个\n    \n      \n        表达式的结果是什么?\n      \n      \n\t语句的结果是什么?\n      \n    假设按照展现的顺序来评估这一序列。\n","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":3,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsoAwDcQA","body":"10; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":4,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsFZQBqUAZiNABYBuIA","body":"5 + 3 + 4; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":5,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsE5QBaVAbiA","body":"9 - 1; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":6,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChudGAEwDcQA","body":"6 / 2; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":7,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsCZQAqUAFlAGpQAKMgWlEwEoBuIA","body":"2 * 4 + (4 - 6); "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":8,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsGMB7AOwGcAXUAQ1AF5QBmAbiA","body":"const a = 3; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":9,"eval":true,"prependLength":3,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsGMB7AOwGcAXUAQ1AF5QBmAbl0NIoCNarQBqVRoA","body":"const b = a + 1; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":10,"eval":true,"prependLength":5,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsGMB7AOwGcAXUAQ1AF5QBmAbl0NIoCNarQBqVZ7NT6c+1AFSh2jIA","body":"a + b + a * b; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":11,"eval":true,"prependLength":5,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsGMB7AOwGcAXUAQ1AF5QBmAbl0NIoCNarQBqVZ7NRrDQ7RkA","body":"a === b; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":12,"eval":true,"prependLength":5,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsGMB7AOwGcAXUAQ1AF5QBmAbl0NIoCNarQBqVZ7JwB83AGSjQnADzcAVJNAB+BQC4qjIA","body":"b > a && b < a * b ? b : a; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":13,"eval":true,"prependLength":5,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsGMB7AOwGcAXUAQ1AF5QBmAbl0NIoCNarQBqVZ7NRrDQAFmwB+UDgBcoTsLripmXqADsaytjkAmAKyMgA","body":"a === 4\n? 6\n: b === 4\n? 6 + 7 + a\n: 25; "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":14,"eval":true,"prependLength":5,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsGMB7AOwGcAXUAQ1AF5QBmAbl0NIoCNarQBqVZ7ACZeoABScAfNwD8oTgC4qASkZA","body":"2 + (b > a ? b : a); "},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":15,"eval":true,"prependLength":5,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsGMB7AOwGcAXUAQ1AF5QBmAbl0NIoCNarQBqVZ7AApqAPlDtsoAPxVJALm4AecZJkTQCgLQoAlNgBUQ6n12MgA","body":"(a > b\n ? a\n : a < b\n ? b\n : -1)\n*\n(a + 1); "},{"body":"\n     \n\t括号围绕条件表达式在最后两个语句中是必要的，因为\n\t\n\t条件表达式的语法形式优先级低于\n\t\n\t算术运算符\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"+"},{"body":" 和\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"*"},{"body":"。\n\n     \n    以下是\n    \n      \n\t表达式。\n      \n      \n\t语句。\n      \n    解释器对每个\n    \n      \n        表达式的结果是什么？\n      \n      \n\t语句的结果是什么？\n      \n    假设按照展现的顺序评估这一序列。\n","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"\n\n   \n    将以下表达式翻译成 \n    \n      \n        前缀形式\n      \n      \n        JavaScript\n      \n    \n      $\\begin{array}{l}\n      \\quad~~\\dfrac{5+4+\\left(2-\\left(3-(6+\\frac{4}{5})\\right)\\right)}{3 (6-2) (2-7)}\n      \\end{array}$\n    \n    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 1.1","id":"#ex-1.1","child":[{"body":"\n      \n        定义一个过程\n      \n      \n\t声明一个函数\n      \n    接收三个数字作为参数并返回两个较大数字的平方和。\n    larger_two_square_example\n      \n(f 4 7 2)\n      \n      \nf(4, 7, 2);\n      ","tag":"#text"}],"solution":[{"body":"\nfunction f(x, y, z) {\n   return square(x) + square(y) + square(z) -\n          // subtract the square of the smallest\n          square(x > y ? (y > z ? z : y) : (x > z ? z : x));\n}\n        \n        \n(define (f x y z)\n   (let ((smallest (if (> x y) (if (> y z) z y) (if (> x z) z x))))\n      (- (+ (square x) (square y) (square z)) (square smallest))))\n        \n      \n    ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 1.4","id":"#ex-1.4","child":[{"body":" \n\t注意我们的评估模型允许\n\t\n\t应用程序，这些应用程序的函数表达式是复合表达式。利用这一观察描述 \n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a_plus_abs_b"},{"body":" 的行为：\n","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":16,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQAHAGwIGcAKAQwBpQAjASlABvUACcApmQIja7UAGpeAblABfXIVKUaoALYUiLDt35DREqTNABaJavXFy1GQH1GLZ+x7NnPI7wGC2KDBZpLSoKw8oAB8ALygAAygAPz0TMygAFy6+ix8fvyK2GrY7K7pHl4+rACs3FYALHyKQA","body":"function plus(a, b) { return a + b; }\n\nfunction minus(a, b) { return a - b; }\n\nfunction a_plus_abs_b(a, b) {\n    return (b >= 0 ? plus : minus)(a, b);\n} "},{"body":"\n\t \n\t请注意，在 JavaScript 中的条件表达式中，我们不能像在 Scheme 中那样直接使用运算符 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"+"},{"body":" 和\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"-"},{"body":"，反而必须使用名称 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"plus"},{"body":" 和\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"minus"},{"body":"，因为在中缀表示法中，\n\t只允许运算符符号出现在中间，而不允许复合表达式。\n \n\t根据节 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"1.1.5","href":"/sicpjs/1.1.5"},{"body":"，应用程序的求值过程如下：\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"OL","child":[{"tag":"LI","child":[{"body":"评估应用程序的子表达式。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"LI","child":[{"body":"评估函数表达式的返回表达式，每个参数都替换为其各自参数表达式的结果。","tag":"#text"}]}]},{"body":"\n\t因此，应用程序 \n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a_plus_abs_b(5, -4)"},{"body":" 的求值 \n\t(1) 评估 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a_plus_abs_b"},{"body":"，得到上面的函数，且参数已是值。所以我们需要评估 \n\t(2) 函数的返回表达式，用参数替换为参数，从而得到：\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"(-4 >= 0 ? plus : minus)(5, -4)"},{"body":"。根据相同规则，我们需要 (1) 评估函数表达式，在本例中是条件表达式 \n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"-4 >= 0 ? plus : minus"},{"body":"。由于谓词评估为假，函数表达式 \n\t评估为 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"minus"},{"body":"。参数再次 (1) 已是值。因此，我们最终评估 (2) ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"minus"},{"body":" 的主体，参数 \n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"a"},{"body":" 和 \n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"b"},{"body":" 分别替换为 5 和 -4，结果为 \n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"5 - (-4)"},{"body":"，最终结果为 9。\n","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"EXERCISE","title":"Exercise 1.5","id":"#ex-1.5","child":[{"body":" \n    Ben Bitdiddle 发明了一项测试，用于判断他面对的解释器是使用 \n    \n    或正则序求值。他 \n    \n      \n\t定义了以下两个过程：\n      \n      \n\t声明了以下两个函数：\n      ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":17,"eval":true,"prependLength":0,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQAHACgEpQBvUAJwFMyCPbGTANygAvrkKlKNUGS4BnMgwAeAGlABPFq2yg9nHn1rLQAXnOgADKAD8V0AC5NQ7KKA","body":"function p() { return p(); }\n\nfunction test(x, y) {\n    return x === 0 ? 0 : y;\n} "},{"body":"\n       \n    然后他评估\n    \n\t表达式\n\t语句","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"SNIPPET","latex":false,"id":18,"eval":true,"prependLength":7,"program":"chap=1&prgrm=PTAEGUEkGEAVQFLlARgHToGwChsDMBXAOwGMAXASwHsjQAHACgEpQBvUAJwFMyCPbGTANygAvrkKlKNUGS4BnMgwAeAGlABPFq2yg9nHn1rLQAXnOgADKAD8V0AC5NQ7OOxzFDS+sHCgA","body":"test(0, p()); "},{"body":"\n       \n\t贝恩·比特迪尔发明了一项测试，用于确定他所面对的解释器是使用\n    \n    应用序求值还是正则序求值。他\n    \n      \n        定义了以下两个过程：\n      \n      \n        声明了以下两个函数：\n      \n \n\t解决方案：\n\t\n\t    在\n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"test(0, p())"},{"body":" 的应用序求值中，\n\t    我们需要在评估函数\n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"test"},{"body":" 的返回表达式之前，先评估参数表达式。\n\t    然而，参数表达式\n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"p()"},{"body":" 的评估不会终止：它将不断评估形如 \n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"p()"},{"body":" 的应用表达式，因此 \n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"test(0, p())"},{"body":" 的评估不会产生合法值。另一方面，在正则序求值中，\n\t    函数应用\n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"test(0, p())"},{"body":" 将立即评估函数\n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"test"},{"body":" 的返回表达式\n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x === 0 ? 0 : y"},{"body":"，\n\t    替换参数 \n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"x"},{"body":" 为 \n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"0"},{"body":" 和 \n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"y"},{"body":" 为 \n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"p()"},{"body":"。\n\t    替换的结果将是\n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"0 === 0 ? 0 : p()"},{"body":"。\n\t    谓词 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"0 === 0"},{"body":" 的评估结果为真，因此条件表达式评估为 0，而不需要评估 \n\t    ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"JAVASCRIPTINLINE","body":"p()"},{"body":"。\n\t  ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-1","count":1,"href":"/sicpjs/1.1.6#footnote-link-1","child":[{"body":"\n\t条件语句\n\t\n\t在完整的 JavaScript 中接受任何值，而不仅仅是布尔值，作为评估\n\t","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"META","body":"谓词"},{"body":" 表达式的结果（有关详细信息，请参见脚注 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":1,"href":"/sicpjs/4.1.3#footnote-1"},{"body":"\n\t在节 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":"4.1.3","href":"/sicpjs/4.1.3"},{"body":"中）。本书中的程序\n\t仅使用布尔值作为条件的谓词。\n      ","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-2","count":2,"href":"/sicpjs/1.1.6#footnote-link-2","child":[{"body":"这一假设是由脚注中提到的限制所证明的 \n\t     ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"REF","body":1,"href":"/sicpjs/1.1.6#footnote-1"},{"body":"。完整的 JavaScript 需要考虑评估 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"META","body":"表达式"},{"body":"$_1$ 的结果既不是 true 也不是 false 的情况。","tag":"#text"}]},{"tag":"DISPLAYFOOTNOTE","id":"#footnote-3","count":3,"href":"/sicpjs/1.1.6#footnote-link-3","child":[{"body":"语法形式只是那些可以用更统一的方式编写的方便替代表面结构，有时称为 ","tag":"#text"},{"tag":"EM","child":[{"body":"语法糖","tag":"#text"}]},{"body":"，这个短语源自 \n            \n\t    Peter Landin。\t    \n\t    ","tag":"#text"}]}]